Day 71: Configure Jenkins Job for Package Installation

Date: November 5, 2025
Overview
Created my first Jenkins job to automate package installation.
Key Concepts Learned

Freestyle projects
Build steps
Shell command execution
Build triggers

Commands Used
bash# In Jenkins build step
sudo yum install -y httpd
sudo systemctl start httpd

Challenges Faced
Permission issues! Jenkins user needed sudo access for package installation.
